# BCDT Project Standards

**AI:** Khi bắt đầu task, đọc [docs/AI_CONTEXT.md](../../docs/AI_CONTEXT.md) (và rule **bcdt-ai-context** nếu cần chi tiết) để nắm ngữ cảnh, tìm đúng tài liệu và giảm token.

## Architecture
- Layered: API → Application → Domain → Infrastructure
- Hybrid data access: EF Core 8 (CRUD) + Dapper (queries, bulk)
- Hybrid storage: JSON (presentation) + Relational (query)

## Naming
- Tables: `BCDT_` prefix (e.g., `BCDT_FormDefinition`)
- API: `/api/v1/{resource}` RESTful
- Services: `I{Name}Service` + `{Name}Service`
- DTOs: `{Entity}Dto`, `{Entity}Request`, `{Entity}Response`

## Patterns
- Repository + Unit of Work for EF Core
- Result<T> pattern (no exceptions for business logic)
- CQRS-lite: Commands mutate, Queries read-only

## Key Tables (44 total)
- Organization: 4 tables (OrganizationType, Organization, User, UserOrganization)
- Authorization: 9 tables (Role, Permission, RolePermission, UserRole, Menu, RoleMenu, DataScope, RoleDataScope, UserDelegation)
- Form: 8 tables (FormDefinition, FormVersion, FormSheet, FormColumn, FormRow, FormCell, FormDataBinding, FormColumnMapping)
- Data: 5 tables (ReportSubmission, ReportPresentation, ReportDataRow, ReportSummary, ReportDataAudit)

## Don't
- Don't put domain logic in controllers
- Don't return EF entities from API (use DTOs)
- Don't use stored procedures for business logic
- Don't bypass Row-Level Security
